GSE45838BCL6BCL6

BCL6 = Ex[, 4:6]
NT = Ex[, 1:3]
signature = rowTtest(BCL6, NT)
signature <- (qnorm(signature$p.value/2, lower.tail = FALSE) *sign(signature$statistic))[, 1]
nullmodel = ttestNull(BCL6, NT, per = 1000, repos = TRUE, seed = 1, verbose = FALSE)
mrs <- msviper(signature, regulon, nullmodel = NULL, verbose = FALSE, pleiotropy = TRUE)
options(repr.plot.width=6, repr.plot.height=10, repr.plot.res = 200)
plot(mrs, 20, cex = .7)

tfMx <- viper(Ex, regulon, dnull = NULL, method = "rank", verbose = FALSE, pleiotropy = TRUE)
